question: Will Josh Dobbs start for the Vikings in Week 14?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Josh Dobbs is the starting quarterback for the Minnesota Vikings in the Week 14 game of the current NFL regular season, which is scheduled to be on December 10, 2023. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If Week 14's game is postponed or cancelled, this market will resolve to 'No'.

The primary resolution source will be official information from the NFL or the Minnesota Vikings.

question: Will Shein IPO at a $90b valuation?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if, by June 30, 2024 ET, Shein completes an Initial Public Offering (IPO) and the company's market capitalization is $90 billion or more at the close of the first day of trading.

In the case of Shein merging with another company, being acquired, or ceasing to exist before the market resolves, this market will resolve to "No".

This market can resolve early if Shein completes an IPO and the company's market capitalization is confirmed to be $90 billion or more before June 30, 2024 ET.

The resolution source for this market is a consensus of credible reporting.

question: Will the Palestinian Authority gain control of Gaza in 2023?
description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if the Palestinian Authority (PA) assumes de jure political control of Gaza by December 31, 2023, 11:59 PM IST (Israel Standard Time). Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from involved governments and IGOs, including the PA, Israel, and the UN, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.
